periya &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; mappillai ( english : groom from a rich place ) is a 1997 tamil comedy film directed by guru dhanapal . the film features jayaram , goundamani , manivannan , devayani and mantra in lead roles . the film , produced by k. murugan , had musical score by sirpy and was released on 22 august 1997 . the film is a remake of the malayalam film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; bava chetan bava .